08:47.337 --> 08:53.832
(Old McDonald had
a farm E-I-E-I-O)

08:51.908 --> 08:54.200
Yeah, well, we finally found
a garage where we can fix it.

08:54.596 --> 08:55.841
We had to take a detour.

09:01.257 --> 09:03.000
...ocean of hatred...

09:02.756 --> 09:04.273
Feel like I'm
back in D.C.

09:03.737 --> 09:05.680
...in our great
nation, and yet,

09:05.885 --> 09:08.550
we all know that these
divisions pale in comparison

09:08.557 --> 09:11.752
to the fundamental dangers
posed by the threat of terror.

09:12.375 --> 09:14.350
We have an eternal
commitment to leave the world

09:14.357 --> 09:16.712
a better place for our
children and grandchildren.

09:16.717 --> 09:20.640
This has always been our
promise and this will always...

09:19.301 --> 09:24.726
Five, four,
three, two, one.

09:28.329 --> 09:30.307
We'll be back in
an hour, Mr. McVey.

