bed. --Honey, stop that. It's my kid.

19:18.856 --> 19:22.160
--Baby, what are you staring at out the
window? --Get over here and look at this!

19:23.036 --> 19:24.220
What-What is that?

19:24.457 --> 19:27.073
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

