--How could we lose
power? --I don't know.

20:08.796 --> 20:09.920
Bomb could have
fried the relays.

20:09.925 --> 20:11.131
--That's
possible. --Maybe.

20:11.488 --> 20:13.580
They could've blown up the
power station for all we know.

20:13.605 --> 20:17.750
Guys, it was probably just a
drain on the system from Denver.

20:19.088 --> 20:21.611
You a science teacher?

20:22.556 --> 20:24.612
--Robert Hawkins.
--Chief Carroll.

20:24.618 --> 20:26.232
--Hey.
--Hey.

20:33.375 --> 20:34.850
Jimmy, what's your 20?

20:35.286 --> 20:36.650
Willow Creek, Sheriff.

20:36.655 --> 20:38.493
There is
nothing in sight.

20:47.435 --> 20:51.601
The deer went crazy and started
running all over the road.

20:52.205 --> 20:53.751
All right, just
don't look at it.

21:02.957 --> 21:03.813
Is he alive?

21:04.648 --> 21:05.461
Yeah.

21:06.178 --> 21:08.931
